{"tid":1917773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧連續兩天說「武漢病毒」　耿爽：譴責這種卑劣做法","createTime":"2020-03-09T16:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T10:29:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":227,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2bd774028da3301ca72aa56ff151201cd0e576","tid":1917773,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T16:14:54.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧上周連續兩天公開說「武漢病毒」及「武漢冠狀病毒」，中國外交部發言人耿爽周一表示，個別美國政客不尊重科學，借新冠病毒對中國和武漢污名化，中方譴責這種「卑劣做法」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%80%BF%E7%88%BD-20200309203018_2cc5_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%2580%25BF%25E7%2588%25BD-20200309203018_2cc5_large.jpg&h=8217a5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧上周五（6日）在美國CNBC訪問談到武漢肺炎疫情說：「請謹記這是武漢冠狀病毒所造成的」（remember this is the Wuhan coronavirus that's caused this）。在之前一天的記者會，蓬佩奧說美國對受到武漢病毒擴散（the Wuhan virus's spread）國家援助3700萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n在周一的記者會上，有記者問耿爽對蓬佩奧上述談話的反應。耿爽說，「世界衛生組織已經就新型冠狀病毒作出正式命名。個別美國政客不尊重科學，不尊重世衛組織的決定，迫不及待地借新冠病毒對中國和武漢進行污名化，我們譴責這種卑劣的做法」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社則報道，世界衛生組織並未就造成今次疫情的病毒名稱定名，而是將疾病名稱定名為2019年冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）。<br />\n<br />\n此外，記者會上有記者問，蓬佩奧還稱由於中方不公開、不透明，美方獲得的信息不完善，導致美方應對疫情挑戰滯後，問中方對此有何評論。耿爽稱，「新冠肺炎疫情發生以後，中方始終本着公開、透明、負責任態度，及時向世衛組織以及包括美國在內的有關國家和地區通報疫情信息，分享病毒基因序列，積極回應各方關切，加強同各方合作。中國為全世界抗擊疫情贏得了時間，作出了積極貢獻。對於這一點，全世界看得清清楚楚，國際社會自有公論。蓬佩奧詆毀中國抗擊疫情努力的企圖不會得逞」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27697/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E8%80%BF%E7%88%BD-27702/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E3%80%91%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%AA%AA%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E3%80%8D-%E8%80%BF%E7%88%BD%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E9%80%99%E7%A8%AE%E5%8D%91%E5%8A%A3%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F27697%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E8%2580%25BF%25E7%2588%25BD-27702%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E3%2580%258D-%25E8%2580%25BF%25E7%2588%25BD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E9%2580%2599%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%258D%2591%25E5%258A%25A3%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%25B3%2595&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM8RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=eab3e00c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/27697/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E8%80%BF%E7%88%BD-27702/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E3%80%91%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%AA%AA%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E3%80%8D-%E8%80%BF%E7%88%BD%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E9%80%99%E7%A8%AE%E5%8D%91%E5%8A%A3%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95</a>"},{"pid":"8b248b66754d586aafb1ee3f54512035f657dc2a","tid":1917773,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2020/03/%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%80%BF%E7%88%BD-20200309203018_2cc5_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%